name: Bench Macro
[Shiny Hunt]
Bench Macro [Shiny Hunt]
desc: Position yourself with your back to the bench you've chosen to sit on, as if you were just killing time. Press L+R+A to activate the macro, holding these buttons for one second to start the loop.
